===Verb===
{{en-verb|spit|ing}}

# {{transitive}} {{obsolete}} To be [[angry]] at; to [[hate]].
# {{transitive}} To treat [[malicious]]ly; to try to [[injure]] or [[thwart]].
#:''She soon married again, to '''spite''' her ex-husband."
# {{transitive}} To fill with spite; to [[offend]]; to [[vex]].

